        "原典: Rosen RC, et al. Development and evaluation of an abridged, 5-item version of the International Index of Erectile Function (IIEF-5) as a diagnostic tool for erectile dysfunction. Int J Impot Res. 1999;11(6):319-326.",
        "国際勃起機能スコア5項目版による勃起機能障害の評価・診断用問診票"
